<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْمَسَدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {تَبَّتْ يَدَا أَبِي لَهَبٍ وَتَبَّ <span class="c2">(١)</span> مَا أَغْنَى عَنْهُ مَالُهُ وَمَا كَسَبَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> سَيَصْلَى نَارًا ذَاتَ لَهَبٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَامْرَأَتُهُ حَمَّالَةَ الْحَطَبِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> فِي جِيدِهَا حَبْلٌ مِنْ مَسَدٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[المسد: ١ - ٥]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">تَبَابٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«خُسْرَانٌ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">تَتْبِيبٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«تَدْمِيرٌ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> حَمَّالَةُ الحَطَبِ: <span class="c2">«تَمْشِي بِالنَّمِيمَةِ»</span>،<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{فِي جِيدِهَا حَبْلٌ مِنْ مَسَدٍ}</span>: <span class="c1">" يُقَالُ: مِنْ مَسَدٍ: لِيفِ المُقْلِ، وَهِيَ السِّلْسِلَةُ الَّتِي فِي النَّارِ "</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>